name: Drunk Skunks Drinking Club
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
STINK Is Main Utility coin of the DSDC Ecosystem.

Owning a Drunk Skunk gets you membership to the Drunk Skunks Drinking Club- a social club with exclusive members only benefits. The Drunk Skunk Drinking Club will include social meetups, merch giveaways, contests and givebacks to our exclusive holders.
Stake your Skunks and earn $STINK

Stake your $STINK and earn $STINK

Use $STINK to mutate your Skunk

Purchase additional NFT DSDC Edition strictly with $STINK
